# {{ project_name | pascal }} - Azure Service Bus Consumer

Auto-generated Go consumer for Azure Service Bus using `github.com/Azure/azure-sdk-for-go/sdk/messaging/azservicebus`.

## Quick start

```go
handler := &My{{ groupname }}Handler{}
consumer, err := {{ project_name | snake }}.New{{ groupname }}Consumer(connectionString, "queue", handler)
if err != nil {
    log.Fatal(err)
}
defer consumer.Close(context.Background())
err = consumer.Start(context.Background())
```

Use `New{{ groupname }}ConsumerForSubscription` for topic subscriptions. Binary CloudEvents are decoded from `ApplicationProperties` with the `cloudEvents:` prefix; structured CloudEvents are decoded from `application/cloudevents+json` message bodies.
